data.description: Seawells Trace in Gloucester,Va! Charming home, excellent location and community to live in and enjoy! Large quarter acre lot offers a rear privacy fence with a tree line border. Home location is one back from neighbor corner lot. Private back yard has space to garden, play, and relax as it features raised garden beds, a children’s play set, and a patio. The foyer is open to the second floor with natural light and spacious with room to welcome guests. The downstairs floor plan offers 9’ ceilings and a great flow from the living area open to the dining room, a kitchen with breakfast nook, and a family room. Family room includes a wood burning fireplace to light for cozy evenings. First floor also includes laundry room and half bath. On the second level there are four generous bedrooms and one currently used as an office.The primary bedroom suite is super spacious with room to create a relaxing get away space or office area. Plus two walk-in closets! The garage offers convenient storage.
